<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Step 3: Your Personality | Amora Hub</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/onboarding.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="onboarding-container">
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-step active">1</div>
            <div class="progress-step active">2</div>
            <div class="progress-step active">3</div>
        </div>
        <div class="onboarding-card">
            <h2>Your Personality</h2>
            <p>Share a little more about yourself to attract the right people.</p>

            <form action="/onboarding/step3" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="work">Work / Occupation</label>
                    <input type="text" id="work" name="work" placeholder="e.g., Software Engineer" required>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="bio">Your Bio</label>
                    <textarea id="bio" name="bio" placeholder="Tell us something interesting about you..." maxlength="500" required></textarea>
                    <p class="input-note">This is your chance to shine. Be authentic!</p>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="interests">Your Interests</label>
                    <input type="text" id="interests" name="interests" placeholder="e.g., Reading, Traveling, Photography">
                    <p class="input-note">Separate interests with a comma.</p>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Finish & View Matches</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>